      "width": 336,
      "height": 120.0,
      "text": "MCP = KNOWLEDGE, read-only.\nIt NEVER writes files or installs.\n\nThe AGENT (Claude Code) does the\nwriting + installing; the MCP just\ntells it what exists & how to use it\ncorrectly - so it can't hallucinate\na component or a prop.",
      "originalText": "MCP = KNOWLEDGE, read-only.\nIt NEVER writes files or installs.\n\nThe AGENT (Claude Code) does the\nwriting + installing; the MCP just\ntells it what exists & how to use it\ncorrectly - so it can't hallucinate\na component or a prop.",
